snippet.title: Asmik-kun Land, NES Longplay
snippet.description:
Asmik-kun Land (アスミッくん ランド Asumikkun Rando') is a Famicom game published by Asmik in 1991.

A cute pink dinosaur named Asmik-kun (named "Boomer" in the English release of Boomer's Adventure in ASMIK World) seeks to recover six fragments so he can wake the dragon ruler of the world and make Asmik Land a paradise.
